          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>bluesign is a comprehensive solution provider for the textile industry, enabling sustainable practices throughout the supply chain. Based on a holistic approach, bluesign follows each textile product right  along its production process and makes improvements at every stage – from manufacturing to the final product. Resource efficiency, consumer  safety, air and water pollution as well as occupational health and safety are monitored. In its role as a solution provider and knowledge mediator, bluesign acts as an independent assessor to ensure trust and transparency. We have entered into this important partnership with bluesign to make our future collections even more environmentally sustainable.</p>"
